### Admin: Get all doctors
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/doctors
Accept: application/json

### Admin: Get doctor by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/doctors/1
Accept: application/json

### Admin: Add a new doctor
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/doctors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Emily",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "email": "emily.smith@example.com",
  "phone": "+1234567890",
  "specialty": "Cardiology",
  "yearsOfExperience": 5,
  "password": "Doctor123!"
}

### Admin: Update doctor by ID
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/doctors/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Emily",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "email": "emily.smith@hospital.com",
  "phone": "+1234567899",
  "specialty": "Cardiology",
  "yearsOfExperience": 6,
  "password": "NewPass123!"
}

### Admin: Remove doctor by ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/admin/doctors/1

### Admin: Get all patients
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/patients
