### Doctor: Get all appointments
GET http://localhost:8080/api/doctor/1/appointments
Accept: application/json

### Doctor: Get appointment by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/doctor/1/appointments/10
Accept: application/json

### Doctor: Mark appointment as completed
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/doctor/1/appointments/10/complete
Accept: application/json

